cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.BIO, cs.HC 

This paper involves the application of machine learning algorithms for multi-class seizure type classification using EEG data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, since the study involves the analysis of EEG data, cs.BIO (Bioinformatics) is also a likely sub-category. Finally, since the study has implications for disease management and patient safety, cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible sub-category.
